&lt;p&gt;PrimeXBT is a Top10 financial services provider offering a wide range of multi-asset trading products, including cryptocurrencies and CFDs. Our proprietary trading platform and integration with MetaTrader 5 (MT5) provide our clients with a robust and versatile trading experience. We are committed to expanding our footprint and are seeking a highly motivated and experienced Business Development Manager to lead this effort.&lt;/p&gt;
