&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Background in business development in Crypto/CFD industry is a must, 2 year +;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent interpersonal and relationship building skills;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Portfolio of partners&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Good verbal and written communication skills .&lt;/li&gt;
