&lt;p&gt;PrimeXBT is a Top10 financial services provider offering a wide range of multi-asset trading products, including cryptocurrencies and CFDs. Our proprietary trading platform and integration with MetaTrader 5 (MT5) provide our clients with a robust and versatile trading experience. We are committed to expanding our footprint &lt;strong&gt;in Nigeria marke&lt;/strong&gt;t and are seeking a highly motivated Business development manager to lead this effort.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for a Business development manager&amp;nbsp;to help scale our global partner ecosystem.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this role, you’ll be responsible for &lt;strong&gt;finding, onboarding, and activating high-quality partners&lt;/strong&gt; who bring new traders to the platform. You’ll own the journey from first contact through activation, working closely with partners to launch campaigns and reach performance milestones.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a &lt;strong&gt;hands-on, performance-driven role&lt;/strong&gt; with a clear impact on growth.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Partner Sourcing &amp;amp; Outreach&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Identify and source potential partners (influencers, educators, communities, agencies)&lt;br&gt;Prospect via LinkedIn, Telegram, YouTube, Instagram, events, and local networks&lt;br&gt;Run structured, personalized outreach across email, messaging apps, and calls&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;Qualification &amp;amp; Deal Management&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Assess partner quality, audience relevance, and growth potential&lt;br&gt;Conduct discovery calls to understand goals and promotion strategies&lt;br&gt;Present partnership models (revenue share, custom deals where applicable)&lt;br&gt;Negotiate terms and agree on short-term performance goals&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;Onboarding &amp;amp; Activation&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Onboard partners into tracking and partner systems&lt;br&gt;Educate partners on tools, tiers, and best practices&lt;br&gt;Support partners in launching their first campaigns&lt;br&gt;Monitor performance and help optimize towards activation&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;Performance Ownership&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Drive partners to reach Active status (5+ first-time deposits)&lt;br&gt;Maintain accurate CRM records and follow-up discipline&lt;br&gt;Handover activated partners to Business Development Managers with full contents&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Operational&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Knowledge of the West Africa region&lt;br&gt;Existing relationship with with active IB&#39;s, Affiliates, Influencers &amp;amp; KOL&#39;s an added advantage&lt;br&gt;Sales driven &amp;amp; self starter&lt;br&gt;Knowledge &amp;amp; experience of the CFD &amp;amp; Crypto industry is must&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What Success Looks Like&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You consistently activate &lt;strong&gt;new high-quality partners&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partners launch campaigns quickly and effectively&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You manage a clean, predictable pipeline&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partners trust you and stay engaged through activation&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We’re Looking For&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Required&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in partnerships, sales, affiliate marketing, or business development within Trading industry.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong communication and negotiation skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfort working with targets and KPIs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Organized, proactive, and follow-up driven&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience using CRMs and digital tools&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nice to Have&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in crypto, fintech, trading, or online platforms&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with influencer or affiliate ecos

