&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Mission of this role:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&quot;This role exists for one purpose: to grow our Crypto business. The Senior Growth Manager&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;will identify and execute disruptive, low-cost initiatives and forge strategic partnerships&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span&gt;that drive meaningful client acquisition within the crypto trading space — combining deep &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;crypto-native intelligence with the ability to mobilise teams without direct authority.&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
