&lt;div class=&quot;textLayer&quot; data-main-rotation=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;▸&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span&gt;Building the intelligence and playbook infrastructure that allows our teams to replicate and scale what &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;works across regions and segments&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span&gt;▸&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span&gt;Positioning our exchange as the go-to platform for both crypto-native power users and the next wave &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;of first-time crypto traders entering the market&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
